cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to '192.168.8.256' with octet 256 out of range will make the NG-AMF unreachable due to invalid IP address.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_RootSequenceIndex to 2048 exceeds the valid range, causing PRACH frequency misalignment and random access failures.
